snippet.title: MotorStorm™RC - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for MotorStorm® mayhem on a whole new scale. Collect and customize your radio controlled cars, compete in high-speed events in classic MotorStorm® locations and challenge your friends on PS3™ and PS Vita.

http://us.playstation.com/games-and-media/games/motorstorm-rc-ps3.html
